<h2>References</h2>

<b>References for Institutional Alternatives
<BR>
</B>
<P>
Akerlof, G., &quot;The Market for Lemons,&quot;
<I>Quarterly Journal of Economics</I>, October 1970, 488-500.
<BR>

<P>
Alchian, A. and William Allen, <I>University
Economics</I>, Belmont, CA: Wadsworth, 1972.<BR>

<P>
Baron, D.P., &quot;Incentive Contracts and
Competitive Bidding,&quot; <I>American Economic Review</I>, 62,
1972, 354-94.<BR>

<P>
Dorfman R. and Peter Steiner, &quot;Optimal
Advertising and Optimal Quality,&quot; <I>American Economic Review</I>,
June 1954, 826-36.<BR>

<P>
Jarrell, G., and Sam Peltzman, &quot;The Impact
of Product Recalls on the Wealth of Sellers,&quot; <I>Journal
of Political Economy</I>, June 1985, 512-36.<BR>

<P>
