http://www.empower.org:80/empower/spring96/trashtv.html 204.71.237.79 19970210103334 text/html 4803
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 10:34:22 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 26-Jul-96 15:32:28 GMT
Content-length: 4620
