<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/pff/aspen-mv.html 204.71.237.79 19970210105709 text/html 16714
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 10:57:56 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jul-96 19:36:21 GMT
Content-length: 16528
